{
  "stem": "9665.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then one week, I was in a Dutch patriotic school with a colonel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Again, I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I get-- ?] also knowing-- wanted to know exactly how I escape from Holland, my experience in Holland, Belgium, and France, and Spain.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So for one week, they kept me there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In the patriotic school, I had the visit of a friend who came also from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "His name was Natan Glatt, G-L-A-T-T.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he came to visit me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "How he found out that I'm in England, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But he was not in the army because he was a scholar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he was at the, the degree of being a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That was Natan Glatt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I can also come back to him, but I don't think that fits into the story.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "After the patriotic school and after being there, I was sent to-- first to Harwich for training, or first-- and then to Dovercourt.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] altogether, we were waiting to be sent to Africa.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We didn't think of Europe at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I made the mistake-- or maybe the right thing-- that I thought that Melitta, who was in America, should come to London.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I started working towards this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And indeed, she came together with Mimi Boers to England and worked at the Dutch government.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Mimi Boers as well-- she worked also for the Dutch government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Barend Boers, as I mentioned before, became my very close friend.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He was also in the Royal Dutch Brigade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he also had his training in Canada.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And it was in the month of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] May, 1944, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that the-- we have picked, 32 people, from the Brigade.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My captain didn't like me at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
